ğŸ’¡ View everything (output + error)
bash
Copy
Edit
grep something file > all.txt 2>&1
ğŸ§ª Use Here String
bash
Copy
Edit
bc <<< "4 * 25"
ğŸ§ª Use Pipe
bash
Copy
Edit
cat list.txt | sort | column
ğŸ§  TL;DR â€“ Power Recap
Symbol	Function
>	Redirect stdout (overwrite)
>>	Redirect stdout (append)
2>	Redirect stderr
&> or > file 2>&1	Redirect all output
<	Redirect stdin
`	`
<<<	Here String
<<EOF	Here Document